# - Development: 5 connections

# Rate Limiting (configured in nginx.conf)
# - API endpoints: 10 requests/second
# - Form submissions: 5 requests/second

# Security Headers (configured in nginx.conf)
# - XSS Protection
# - Content Security Policy
# - Frame Options
# - Referrer Policy

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Deployment Notes
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Copy this file to .env and update values for your environment
# 2. Use strong, unique passwords in production
# 3. Update DB_HOST for your database server
# 4. Configure firewall/security groups for ports:
#    - 80 (HTTP)
#    - 3001 (Grafana)
#    - 8081 (cAdvisor)
#    - 9090 (Prometheus)
# 5. Set NODE_ENV=production for production deployments
# 6. Consider using secrets management for sensitive data
